FBIS4-57115 "drlat093_j_94003" FBIS-LAT-94-093 Daily Report 11 May 1994 Panama Endara, Perez Balladares Appoint Transition Team Endara, Perez Balladares Appoint Transition Team PA1205191094 Panama City Telemetro Television Network in Spanish 1730 GMT 11 May 94 PA1205191094 Panama City Telemetro Television Network Spanish BFN [From the "Telemetro Reports" newscast] [Text] After President-elect Ernesto Perez Balladares announced the designation of Jose Luis Sosa as his representative to the Government Transition Commission, Arnulfista Party sources said President Guillermo Endara has appointed Joaquin Fernando Franco, vice president of the Authentic Liberal Party, and Eduardo Linares, deputy planning and economic policy minister, as his representatives.
